{"title":"盛会即兴（七绝二首）","authors":["关山月"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":3,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛会即兴（七绝二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关山月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国家昌盛要太平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浊水污泥碍进程；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教育方针治好本，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文明两手更文明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年议政灿春花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛世言行暖万家；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赢得黄昏无限好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又看明日红朝霞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１９９５年３月１０日晨"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}